# CODEOWNERS — Automatic PR reviewer assignment
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# Format: <pattern>  <@owner or @org/team>
# Last matching rule wins.

# Default owner for everything
# * @[Project Name]-team

# Core AI configuration — require review for any changes
# AGENTS.md        @[owner]
# docs/context.md  @[owner]
# CLAUDE.md        @[owner]
# GEMINI.md        @[owner]

# Agent definitions — architect or PM must review
# agents/          @[owner]

# Automation scripts — at least one DevOps reviewer
# scripts/         @[owner]
# .githooks/       @[owner]
